+/**
+ * V3 Neural/Learning System Types
+ * Core type definitions for SONA learning modes and ReasoningBank integration
+ *
+ * Performance Targets:
+ * - SONA adaptation: <0.05ms
+ * - Pattern matching: <1ms
+ * - Learning step: <10ms
+ */
